<title>HONG KONG: Bankers Trust sets China Light warrants.</title>
<headline>Bankers Trust sets China Light warrants.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bankers Trust International Plc</p>
<p>said it intended to issue 64 million American style call</p>
<p>warrants on shares of China Light &amp; Power Co Ltd.</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE	HK$28.815    PREMIUM	 8.50 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE	 HK$0.7967    GEARING	 4.2553X</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	  21.NOV.97    PAYDATE	 3 WKS AFTER LAUNCH</p>
<p> LISTING	     HONG KONG    MIN EXER LOT  5,000</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE    HK$33.90</p>
<p> NOTES		 GOVERNING LAW IS HONG KONG</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
</text>
